HEADWORD: Mackinaw coat
<hw>Mack"i*naw coat</hw></mhw>. <def>A short,
heavy, double-breasted plaid coat, the design of which is large and
striking.</def> <mark>[Local, U. S.]</mark>⟦br⟧
